    "body": "Problem: C formatting is enforced in CI via uncrustify, but when working on C code clangd formats on save via clang-format, forcing users to manually run `make formatc` after they're done.\r\n\r\nSolution: disable clang-format.",
    "closed_at": "2026-05-01T14:01:41Z",
